### Low Level API: ChatModel
GET http://localhost:8082/model?message=What is the capital of Germany?

### High Level API: AI Service with tools
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant?message=What is the current time?&sessionId=local-test-session-001

### Assistant history
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant/history?sessionId=local-test-session-001

### Clear in-memory session
DELETE http://localhost:8082/assistant/session/local-test-session-001

### Debug active sessions
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant/debug/sessions
